WEBVTT

00:00:00.753 --> 00:00:02.757
Antes de facerme dermatólogo,

00:00:02.757 --> 00:00:05.319
comecei na medicina xeral,

00:00:05.319 --> 00:00:07.555
como fan moitos dermatólogos
en Gran Bretaña.

00:00:08.064 --> 00:00:09.603
Ao rematar, fun a Australia,

00:00:10.073 --> 00:00:11.639
hai case vinte anos.

00:00:12.089 --> 00:00:13.750
Cando marchas a Australia

00:00:13.750 --> 00:00:16.446
aprendes que os australianos
son moi competitivos.

00:00:16.446 --> 00:00:18.403
E non son magnánimos nas vitorias.

00:00:18.403 --> 00:00:20.467
E iso pasaba moito:

00:00:20.467 --> 00:00:22.899
"Ingleses, non sabedes xogar
ao cricket, rugby...".

00:00:23.559 --> 00:00:25.017
Podía aceptar iso.

00:00:25.907 --> 00:00:27.347
No relacionado ao traballo,

00:00:27.597 --> 00:00:29.885
temos semanalmente
un club de lectura,

00:00:29.885 --> 00:00:32.343
onde sentas cos outros médicos